Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
timing_report_...el_capacitance(25.10)  timing_report_...el_capacitance(25.10)

Name
       timing_report_use_receiver_model_capacitance

Syntax
       timing_report_use_receiver_model_capacitance {true | false}

       Default: false

       Enables  the  max_capacitance  violations  based on dynamic pin capaci-
       tance.

       When set to true, the software checks for both the input level and tim-
       ing arc level dynamic pin capacitance tables for worst-case pin capaci-
       tance table for given input slew. If conditional pin capacitance tables
       (or timing_arcs) exist, the worst-case is used  among  all  the  condi-
       tions.

       This  global  variable  performs static pin capacitance inference after
       delay calculation, so the delay computation is not  impacted.  The  pin
       capacitance is used only for reporting and max_cap violations.

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

